16  Eigen::Vector3d calculateOrientationError(const Eigen::Quaterniond &orientation_d, Eigen::Quaterniond orientation)
17  {
18  // Orientation error
19  if (orientation_d.coeffs().dot(orientation.coeffs()) < 0.0)
20  {
21  orientation.coeffs() << -orientation.coeffs();
22  }
23  // "difference" quaternion
24  const Eigen::Quaterniond error_quaternion(orientation * orientation_d.inverse());
25  // convert to axis angle
26  Eigen::AngleAxisd error_quaternion_angle_axis(error_quaternion);
27  return error_quaternion_angle_axis.axis() * error_quaternion_angle_axis.angle();
28  }

37  template <typename T>
38  T filteredUpdate(T target, T current, double filter)
39  {
40  return (1.0 - filter) * current + filter * target;
41  }

61  void saturateTorqueRate(const Eigen::VectorXd &tau_d_calculated, Eigen::VectorXd *tau_d_saturated, double delta_tau_max)
62  {
63  for (size_t i = 0; i < tau_d_calculated.size(); i++)
64  {
65  const double difference = tau_d_calculated[i] - tau_d_saturated->operator()(i);
66  tau_d_saturated->operator()(i) += saturateValue(difference, -delta_tau_max, delta_tau_max);
67  }
68  }

103  void CartesianImpedanceController::setStiffness(const Eigen::Matrix<double, 7, 1> &stiffness, bool auto_damping)
104  {
105  for (int i = 0; i < 6; i++)
106  {
107  assert(stiffness(i) >= 0.0 && "Stiffness values need to be positive.");
108  // Set diagonal values of stiffness matrix
109  this->cartesian_stiffness_target_(i, i) = stiffness(i);
110  }
111  assert(stiffness(6) >= 0.0 && "Stiffness values need to be positive.");
112  this->nullspace_stiffness_target_ = stiffness(6);
113  if (auto_damping)
114  {
115  this->applyDamping();
116  }
117  }

134  void CartesianImpedanceController::setDamping(double d_x, double d_y, double d_z, double d_a, double d_b, double d_c,
135  double d_n)
136  {
137  Eigen::Matrix<double, 7, 1> damping_new;
138  damping_new << d_x, d_y, d_z, d_a, d_b, d_c, d_n;
139  for (size_t i = 0; i < damping_new.size(); i++)
140  {
141  if (damping_new(i) < 0)
142  {
143  damping_new(i) = this->damping_factors_(i);
144  }
145  }
146  this->damping_factors_ = damping_new;
147  this->applyDamping();
148  }

150  void CartesianImpedanceController::applyDamping()
151  {
152  for (int i = 0; i < 6; i++)
153  {
154  assert(this->damping_factors_(i) >= 0.0 && "Damping values need to be positive.");
155  this->cartesian_damping_target_(i, i) =
156  this->damping_factors_(i) * this->dampingRule(this->cartesian_stiffness_target_(i, i));
157  }
158  this->nullspace_damping_target_ = this->damping_factors_(6) * this->dampingRule(this->nullspace_stiffness_target_);
159  }

202  Eigen::VectorXd CartesianImpedanceController::calculateCommandedTorques(const Eigen::VectorXd &q,
203  const Eigen::VectorXd &dq,
204  const Eigen::Vector3d &position,
205  Eigen::Quaterniond orientation,
206  const Eigen::MatrixXd &jacobian)
207  {
208  // Update controller to the current robot state
209  this->q_ = q;
210  this->dq_ = dq;
211  this->position_ << position;
212  this->orientation_.coeffs() << orientation.coeffs();
213  this->jacobian_ << jacobian;
214 
215  return this->calculateCommandedTorques();
216  }
217 
218  Eigen::VectorXd CartesianImpedanceController::calculateCommandedTorques()
219  {
220  // Perform a filtering step
221  updateFilteredNullspaceConfig();
222  updateFilteredStiffness();
223  updateFilteredPose();
224  updateFilteredWrench();
225 
226  // Compute error term
227  error_.head(3) << this->position_ - this->position_d_;
228  error_.tail(3) << calculateOrientationError(this->orientation_d_, this->orientation_);
229 
230  // Kinematic pseuoinverse
231  Eigen::MatrixXd jacobian_transpose_pinv;
232  pseudoInverse(this->jacobian_.transpose(), &jacobian_transpose_pinv);
233 
234  Eigen::VectorXd tau_task(this->n_joints_), tau_nullspace(this->n_joints_), tau_ext(this->n_joints_);
235 
236  // Torque calculated for Cartesian impedance control with respect to a Cartesian pose reference in the end, in the frame of the EE of the robot.
237  tau_task << this->jacobian_.transpose() * (-this->cartesian_stiffness_ * this->error_ - this->cartesian_damping_ * (this->jacobian_ * this->dq_));
238  // Torque for joint impedance control with respect to a desired configuration and projected in the null-space of the robot's Jacobian, so it should not affect the Cartesian motion of the robot's end-effector.
239  tau_nullspace << (Eigen::MatrixXd::Identity(7, 7) - this->jacobian_.transpose() * jacobian_transpose_pinv) *
240  (this->nullspace_stiffness_ * (this->q_d_nullspace_ - this->q_) - this->nullspace_damping_ * this->dq_);
241  // Torque to achieve the desired external force command in the frame of the EE of the robot.
242  tau_ext = this->jacobian_.transpose() * this->cartesian_wrench_;
243 
244  // Torque commanded to the joints of the robot is composed by the superposition of these three joint-torque signals:
245  Eigen::VectorXd tau_d = tau_task + tau_nullspace + tau_ext;
246  saturateTorqueRate(tau_d, &this->tau_c_, this->delta_tau_max_);
247  return this->tau_c_;
248  }

316  void CartesianImpedanceController::updateFilteredStiffness()
317  {
318  if (this->filter_params_stiffness_ == 1.0)
319  {
320  this->cartesian_stiffness_ = this->cartesian_stiffness_target_;
321  this->cartesian_damping_ = this->cartesian_damping_target_;
322  this->nullspace_stiffness_ = this->nullspace_stiffness_target_;
323  this->q_d_nullspace_ = this->q_d_nullspace_target_;
324  this->nullspace_damping_ = this->nullspace_damping_target_;
325  }
326  else
327  {
328  const double step = this->filter_params_stiffness_ / this->update_frequency_;
329  this->cartesian_stiffness_ = filteredUpdate(this->cartesian_stiffness_target_, this->cartesian_stiffness_, step);
330  this->cartesian_damping_ = filteredUpdate(this->cartesian_damping_target_, this->cartesian_damping_, step);
331  this->nullspace_stiffness_ = filteredUpdate(this->nullspace_stiffness_target_, this->nullspace_stiffness_, step);
332  this->nullspace_damping_ = filteredUpdate(this->nullspace_damping_target_, this->nullspace_damping_, step);
333  }
334  }
335 
336  void CartesianImpedanceController::updateFilteredPose()
337  {
338  if (filter_params_pose_ == 1.0)
339  {
340  position_d_ << position_d_target_;
341  orientation_d_.coeffs() << orientation_d_target_.coeffs();
342  }
343  else
344  {
345  const double step = this->filter_params_pose_ / this->update_frequency_;
346  this->position_d_ = filteredUpdate(this->position_d_target_, this->position_d_, step);
347  this->orientation_d_ = this->orientation_d_.slerp(step, this->orientation_d_target_);
348  }
349  }

351  void CartesianImpedanceController::updateFilteredWrench()
352  {
353  const double step = this->filter_params_wrench_ / this->update_frequency_;
354  this->cartesian_wrench_ = filteredUpdate(this->cartesian_wrench_target_, this->cartesian_wrench_, step);
355  }
